RD_ttns11usK4KVtEufiWIcVUIvlrb4W8bQiCX2x6l-nCrExX3vkc8If6FlZXlx-AHpXB72S_Ky311SgrftjfMn_wQnNgX74cy5IaB9K04J1IiIf5mkNgBKHFRjM-AfQXBBEVOQ_BRF_-DbNbIWl9CBLo_sURg2rZaYlD4eaEH5nGb04VPESyQ9V5Lzkw_RzjU2H89vq5SHxR0o-LgNJiaR0=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating API Mapping**\\n\\nI'm trying to maintain dynamic access with a one-to-one mapping here. I wonder if I could remove some tests, but that's not the case. I need to replace missing APIs with equivalent existing classes, especially if the class names have changed. I'm looking at the test file named FormatInnerDefaultEscapeStrategyTest related to the inner class in JDOM 1.0. In version b8, there’s no Format, so I should inspect XMLOutputter, as it might have a private inner DefaultEscapeStrategy.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_kvSSW7lkvwmZKD7NEeGgOx6s|fc_0091739b4e8af8f00169fc7b79f4748190bffd1df7b31b3fe1", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge5/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/jdom/jdom/1.0b8/main/extracted/jdom-b8/src/java/org/jdom/output/XMLOutputter.java", "limit": 400}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 984, "output": 167, "cacheRead": 12288, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 13439, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778154357473, "responseId": "resp_0091739b4e8af8f00169fc7b764d7c8190bc6ec03b8258fda2"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_kvSSW7lkvwmZKD7NEeGgOx6s|fc_0091739b4e8af8f00169fc7b79f4748190bffd1df7b31b3fe1", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/*--\r\n\r\n $Id: XMLOutputter.java,v 1.76 2002/03/15 05:36:48 jhunter Exp $\r\n\r\n Copyright (C) 2000 Brett McLaughlin & Jason Hunter.\r\n All rights reserved.\r\n\r\n Redistribution and use in source and binary forms, with or without\r\n modification, are permitted provided that the